OL,3,COne in four fear having to turn off
OL,4,Cheating this winter amid energy bill
OL,5,Cspike
OL,7,FUp to a quarter of the UK population
OL,8,Ffear they may have to turn off their
OL,9,Fheating and hot water this winter due
OL,10,Fto an expected rise in household
OL,11,Fenergy bills, research suggests.
OL,13,FA survey by Citizens Advice found that
OL,14,F31% of households with children and
OL,15,F39% of low-income individuals expect
OL,16,Fto take such drastic action.
