OL,3,COne in four fear having to turn off
OL,4,Cheating this winter amid energy bill
OL,5,Cspike
OL,7,FThe charity, which has seen record
OL,8,Fnumbers of people struggling with
OL,9,Fenergy debt despite lower summer
OL,10,Fcosts, warned that without urgent
OL,11,Fgovernment intervention, households
OL,12,Fwill face "impossible choices and
OL,13,Fdrastic cutbacks" to heat their homes.
OL,15,FOverall, the survey found that 48% of
OL,16,Frespondents stated they would turn
OL,17,Fdown or turn off their heating or
OL,18,Fwater if the energy price cap rises by
OL,19,Fthe 9% predicted by experts.
