OL,7,FA third of households surveyed said it
OL,8,Fwould be difficult to budget food
OL,9,Fcosts and other daily essentials such
OL,10,Fas mortgages, rent and childcare,
OL,11,Fwhile 7% said they would be forced to
OL,12,Fskip meals.
OL,14,FEnergy consultancy firm Cornwall
OL,15,FInsight recently estimated that the
OL,16,Fenergy price cap will rise on October
OL,17,F1, increasing a typical household's
OL,18,Fannual bill from #1,568 to #1,714.
