OL,7,FEnergy regulator Ofgem is expected to
OL,8,Fconfirm the new energy price cap for
OL,9,FOctober to December on Friday.
OL,11,FCitizens Advice said 7% of households
OL,12,Fcurrently remain in debt to their
OL,13,Fenergy supplier. The proportion rises
OL,14,Fto 14% for households with children
OL,15,Fdespite last year's slight reduction
OL,16,Fin bills.
