OL,4,Cheating this winter amid energy bill
OL,5,Cspike
OL,7,FThe charity stated that essential
OL,8,Fmonthly outgoings exceed the incomes
OL,9,Fof about five million people, and the
OL,10,Fexpected price cap increase is
OL,11,Fprojected to push an additional
OL,12,F187,000 people into a negative budget.
OL,14,FCitizens Advice urged the government
OL,15,Fto "act fast" to prevent millions of
OL,16,Fhouseholds from experiencing further
OL,17,Fhardship this winter, with those in
OL,18,F"desperate need" unable to wait for
OL,19,FLabour's long-term goal of reducing
OL,20,Fcosts through a greater focus on
OL,21,Frenewables.
