OL,7,FDame Clare Moriarty, chief executive
OL,8,Fof Citizens Advice, said the charity
OL,9,Fis "bracing" itself for a "challenging
OL,10,Fwinter".
OL,12,FShe added: "The price cap increase
OL,13,Fwill see a wave of households tipped
OL,14,Finto debt, bill payers forced to make
OL,15,Fimpossible decisions to make ends
OL,16,Fmeet, and families worried about the
OL,17,Fimpact the cold will have on their
OL,18,Floved ones.
