OL,7,F"Energy prices might be down from the
OL,8,Fpeak of the crisis, but with many
OL,9,Falready in the red and the removal of
OL,10,Fprevious support packages, there's
OL,11,Fstill no light at the end of the
OL,12,Ftunnel for those in desperate need.
OL,14,F"The Government has inherited a huge
OL,15,Fchallenge, so there must be no delay
OL,16,Fin their action.
OL,18,F"We need to see targeted bill support
OL,19,Fthat reflects the realities of
OL,20,Fpeople's energy needs."
